Pw*alert*topbox.orientation:		vertical
Pw*alert*buttonbox.orientation:		horizontal

Pw*listshell*borderWidth:		0
Pw*listshell*topbox.orientation:	horizontal
Pw*listshell*listbox.orientation:	vertical
